where formula_4 is the density of the mantle (ca. 3,300 kg m−3), formula_5 is the density of the crust (ca. 2,750 kg m−3) and formula_11 is the density of the water (ca. 1,000 kg m−3). Thus, generally:

:&quot;b&quot;2 ≅ 3.2⋅&quot;h&quot;2

